","article",null,{"className":"prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"text-white/80 leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-line mb-10","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"A gas engineer who misses calls while working loses roughly £30,000 per year in recoverable revenue. I am Mark Harrison, 41, Gas Safe registered, Walthamstow. Nine years self-employed. Wife, two kids, mortgage. I worked out the maths properly — not guesses, actual numbers — and I was furious. Then I tried AI call answering for four weeks and tracked every penny. Here is exactly what happened."}}],["$L24","$L25","$L26","$L27","$L28","$L29","$L2a","$L2b","$L2c","$L2d","$L2e","$L2f","$L30","$L31","$L32","$L33"],"$L34","$L35","$L36","$L37"]}]]}]
