36:["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6","children":"Frequently Asked Questions"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-4","children":[["$","div","faq-0",{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"How much does an AI receptionist cost for a gas engineer?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed","children":"whoza.ai's Starter plan costs £59 per month for pay-per-job pricing. That is less than the profit on one average gas engineering job. Most users break even within 48 hours of setup."}]]}],["$","div","faq-1",{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"Can AI really understand emergency boiler calls?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed","children":"Yes. Katie identifies emergency keywords — no heating, no hot water, gas leak, carbon monoxide alarm — and flags them immediately in the WhatsApp summary. She also asks the right qualifying questions to determine urgency and timeline."}]]}],["$","div","faq-2",{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"Do customers know they are talking to AI?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed","children":"Most callers cannot tell. Katie uses natural language and a human-like voice. Customers care about getting their problem solved quickly, not about who answers. Several of my customers complimented 'my receptionist' on being helpful."}]]}],["$","div","faq-3",{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"What happens to emergency calls with AI answering?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed","children":"Emergency calls are answered instantly, qualified, and delivered to your WhatsApp with an urgent flag. Katie asks about the severity and confirms whether it is a safety issue. You see it immediately and can call back within minutes."}]]}],["$","div","faq-4",{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"Is a 7-day free trial actually free?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed","children":"Yes. No credit card required. No contract. You sign up, connect your number, and test it for a full week. If you do not capture any value, you walk away with zero cost. Most users see their first captured job within 24 hours."}]]}],["$","div","faq-5",{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"How quickly can I get set up?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed","children":"Under 10 minutes. Connect your existing number via call forwarding, set your greeting and business details, and Katie starts answering immediately. No technical knowledge required. If you can use a smartphone, you can set this up."}]]}],["$","div","faq-6",{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3","children":"What happens if Katie cannot handle a call?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed","children":"Katie captures the core details — name, number, address, and issue — even in difficult cases. If a call is truly complex, she takes a message and flags it for your immediate attention. You never miss the information, even if Katie cannot fully resolve the enquiry."}]]}],"$L3e"]}]]}]
